OL,3,CFormer Conservative MP pleads guilty
OL,4,Cto harassing ex-wife
OL,6,FA former Conservative MP has pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to the harassment of their ex-
OL,8,Fwife.
OL,10,FKatie Wallis, 41, of Butetown,
OL,11,FCardiff, admitted the "harassment
OL,12,Fwithout violence" of Rebecca Wallis
OL,13,Fbetween February and March this year,
OL,14,Fhaving left her a number of messages
OL,15,Fand a voice note.
OL,17,FWallis, who was previously known as
OL,18,FJamie, was the MP for Bridgend from
OL,19,F2019 to 2024.
