OL,3,CFormer Conservative MP pleads guilty
OL,4,Cto harassing ex-wife
OL,6,FAt Cardiff Magistrates' Court on
OL,7,FTuesday, 17 June, District Judge Rhys
OL,8,FWilliams accepted a basis of plea.
OL,10,FWallis pleaded guilty to leaving the
OL,11,Fmessages, but allegations of having
OL,12,Fdriven by their ex-wife's home were
OL,13,Fremoved from the charge.
OL,15,FWallis will next appear before the
OL,16,Fcourt on July 14 for sentencing.
OL,18,FNarita Bahra KC, appearing for the
OL,19,Fdefence, said her client did not wish
OL,20,Fto put their former partner, or their
OL,21,Ffamilies, through anything further.
