OL,6,F"He has, on balance, taken the
OL,7,Fpragmatic view, and recognises that he
OL,8,Fhas previously had a public profile
OL,9,Fand taken the view that he can be
OL,10,Frearraigned," she said.
OL,12,FMs Bahra said a psychiatric assessment
OL,13,Fand a pre-sentence report would be
OL,14,Fneeded ahead of sentencing.
OL,16,FShe said this would examine what
OL,17,Fimpact Wallis' gender transition had
OL,18,Fhad on their mental health during the
OL,19,Fperiod the offences occurred.
